<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<package xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/packaging/2015/06/nuspec.xsd">
  <metadata>
    <id>netcheck</id>
    <version>{version}</version>
    <title>NetCheck - Network Intelligence CLI</title>
    <authors>Farman Ali</authors>
    <owners>alienhub</owners>

    <projectUrl>https://github.com/farman20ali/network_access_check</projectUrl>
    <projectSourceUrl>https://github.com/farman20ali/network_access_check/tree/main/netcheck</projectSourceUrl>
    <packageSourceUrl>https://github.com/farman20ali/network_access_check/tree/main/packaging/chocolatey</packageSourceUrl>
    <docsUrl>https://github.com/farman20ali/network_access_check/blob/main/README.md</docsUrl>
    <bugTrackerUrl>https://github.com/farman20ali/network_access_check/issues</bugTrackerUrl>

    <licenseUrl>https://github.com/farman20ali/network_access_check/blob/main/LICENSE</licenseUrl>
    <requireLicenseAcceptance>false</requireLicenseAcceptance>

    <iconUrl>https://raw.githubusercontent.com/farman20ali/network_access_check/main/assets/icons/icon.png</iconUrl>

    <summary>Cross-platform network diagnostics engine — DNS, TCP, HTTP, SSL, ping, MCP</summary>
    <description>A cross-platform network intelligence engine and CLI written in pure Python 3.

Supports:
- DNS lookup (A/AAAA, cached, strict timeouts)
- TCP port connectivity (concurrent scanning)
- HTTP/HTTPS audits (latency, content size, redirects)
- SSL/TLS certificate validation (subject, issuer, expiry warnings)
- ICMP ping (packet loss and RTT stats)
- Network interface enumeration with public IP
- Structured output: text, JSON, CSV, XML
- Model Context Protocol (MCP) server for AI assistants
- Lenient target parsing: URLs, IP ranges, CIDR, port ranges, CSV files

Run `netcheck mcp` to expose network tools to MCP-compatible clients (VS Code Copilot, Cursor, Claude Desktop).

The Windows installer is downloaded from the official GitHub release during installation.</description>

    <releaseNotes>https://github.com/farman20ali/network_access_check/releases/tag/v{version}</releaseNotes>
    <tags>netcheck network ping dns ssl http tcp mcp diagnostic cli tool cross-platform python devops</tags>
  </metadata>
  <files>
    <file src="tools\chocolateyInstall.ps1" target="tools" />
    <file src="tools\chocolateyUninstall.ps1" target="tools" />
  </files>
</package>